OL,3,C2,000 British Steel jobs at risk amid
OL,4,Crumoured plans to close Scunthorpe
OL,5,Cblast furnaces
OL,7,FUp to 2,000 workers could lose their
OL,8,Fjobs amid plans by British Steel to
OL,9,Fclose down the blast furnaces at its
OL,10,FScunthorpe plant, according to
OL,11,Freports.
OL,13,FThe company, which is owned by
OL,14,FChinese firm Jingye, wants to replace
OL,15,Fthem with two electric arc versions
OL,16,Fwhich can run on zero-carbon
OL,17,Felectricity.
OL,19,FIt would build one new electric arc
OL,20,Ffurnace in Scunthorpe, with another
OL,21,Fat its Teesside plant.
